cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the development of autonomous robotic systems and imitation learning between two robotic arms. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a model-free deep reinforcement learning framework for dynamic movement imitation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper deals with learning from human demonstrations and developing autonomous systems. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible category as the paper may involve visual perception for the robotic arms. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with controlling the movements of robotic arms.
